            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Herc</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Invic</abbr><ex>to</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mettius</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> Sabi<lb break="no" n="3"/>nus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I Aeliae <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Athoit</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> et <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Berec</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>luc</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>Herc</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> vo<lb break="no" n="6"/>tum et signum pos<lb break="no" n="7"/>uit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. (B): AE 1919: Z. 1: Invi(cto); Z. 2: Menius; AE 1979, ILBulg: Z. 3/4: Zeilenfall fehlt; AE 1979: Z. 4-6: Athoit(orum), e(t) Berec(ynthorum) lucum devo/tum e(t); ILBulg: Z. 4-6: Athoite / libe(n)s(?) iuc(unde) Herc(uli)(?) vo/tum et.</p>
            </div>
